Package: hyper.gam
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Additive Models with Hyper Column
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-03
Description: Generalized additive models with a numeric hyper column tabulated on a common grid. Sign-adjustment based on the correlation of model prediction and a user-selected slice of the hyper column. Visualization of the integrand surface over the hyper column.
